<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-cta">
  <h1 class="header1">Pantry Hacker</h1>
  <p>
    Ever come home from a long day of work and stare blankly in your fridge thinking what to make? You've come to the right place. Pantry Hacker allow a user to input indregients they already have in their fridge and provide meal options in seconds. You can also create a account to post your own recipes as well as comment on your favorites? Give it a try below...
</p>
